(2604, 7, 'content1', '<h4 class="service_title">World-Class Facility</h4>\r\n<span class="cc">With Good Samaritan Retirement Home, your elderly loved ones are under expert care. Our <a href="http://goodsamalf.com/" class="service_links"><u>assisted living</u></a> and memory care residents are given the loving attention they deserve. Our facilities are carefully designed with their needs in mind. We always keep in mind their need for holistic health, emotional well being, and physical comfort.</span>'),
(2605, 7, 'content2', '<h4 class="service_title">Convenient Location Image</h4>\r\n<span class="cc">\r\nOur assisted living and memory care facility is conveniently nestled \r\nbetween <a href="http://goodsamalf.com/" class="service_links"><u>Gainsville</u></a> and <a href="http://goodsamalf.com/" class="service_links"><u>Ocala, Florida</u></a>. It is minutes away from the airport and situated a few blocks from hospitals, hotels, and academic institutions.\r\n</span>'),
(1719, 259, 'about_us_intro', 'As a people, we perceive caring for our mothers, fathers and grandparents in their golden years not as mere duty, but as an opportunity to lavish them with the love they had once provided us.  At Good Samaritan Retirement Home , we take this same mission to heart.  We will strive to make your stay as enjoyable as possible, in a home where everything is sufficiently provided for. Our ultimate goal is to help you perform the task of daily living easier, safer and even enjoyable. '),
