(2722, 442, 'about_us_intro', 'At Good Samaritan Retirement Home, we believe that caring is all about relationships. This is why we foster an environment that strengthens the bonds of family love. We understand that as humans, caring for our elderly is above one''s duty. It is a chance to give back and show them the love they showered us throughout our lives. '),
