(2606, 7, 'content3', '<h4 class="service_title">Compassionate and <br />Dedicated Staff</h4>\r\n<span class="cc">\r\nGood Samaritan Retirement Home is a family of <a href="http://goodsamalf.com/" class="service_links"><u>dedicated healthcare professionals</u></a> who understands the value of nurturing and caring for the elderly. It is an assisted living facility nestled between <a href="http://goodsamalf.com/" class="service_links"><u>Ocala</u></a> and <a href="http://goodsamalf.com/" class="service_links"><u>Gainsville, Florida</u></a>. Our team''s combined healthcare service experiences are coupled with compassion, a formula that delivers the <a href="http://goodsamalf.com/" class="service_links"><u>best assisted living</u></a> and memory care.\r\n</span>'),
(2607, 7, 'content4', '<h4 class="service_title">Expert Care</h4>\r\n<span class="cc">\r\nOur facility provides a comforting environment for our elderly loved ones who battle the burdens of <a href="http://goodsamalf.com/" class="service_links"><u>dementia</u></a> and <a href="http://goodsamalf.com/" class="service_links"><u>alzheimer''s</u></a>. They are supported by a team of caring and experienced healthcare providers who make your loved ones stay in our facility memorable and safe.\r\n</span>'),
(2608, 7, 'content5', '<h4 class="service_title">Holistic Programs</h4>\r\n<span class="cc">\r\nMore than the nurturing environment, Good Samaritan Retirement Home also <a href="http://goodsamalf.com/" class="service_links"><u>offers healthcare programs</u></a> which are developed to help our residents gain back control of their lives. We have programs that specifically cater to certain medical conditions as well as  <a href="http://goodsamalf.com/" class="service_links"><u>general healthcare programs</u></a>.\r\n</span>'),
