(239, 1, '2017-06-29 04:11:42', '2017-06-29 04:11:42', 'We work with our residents on a personal basis to make sure their specific needs are addressed and appropriately met. Residents of our <a hre="http://goodsamalf.com/goodsamservices/247-warchful-oversight-2/"><u>Good Samaritan Retirement Home</u></a> are afforded as much independence as preferred with the comfort of knowing that personal care and support services are available on site as needed.', '24/7 Watchful Oversight', 'We work with our residents on a personal basis to make sure their specific needs are addressed and appropriately met', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '247-watchful-oversight', '', '', '2017-07-28 13:29:15', '2017-07-28 13:29:15', '', 0, 'http://goodsamalf.com/?post_type=goodsamservices&#038;p=239', 0, 'goodsamservices', '', 0),
(240, 1, '2017-06-29 04:14:19', '2017-06-29 04:14:19', 'Seniors maintaining their independence is crucial for <a href="http://goodsamalf.com/goodsamservices/arrangement-for-transportation-2/"><u>healthy and active aging</u></a>. A big part of independence is transportation. At Good Samaritan Retirement Home we provide a door-to-door system where advance reservations are made to take an elderly individual from one place to another. These services provide comfort, convenience, and flexibility. <a href="http://goodsamalf.com/goodsamservices/arrangement-for-transportation-2/"><u>Fixed route or scheduled services transport for elderly</u></a> individuals between fixed stops on a route.', 'Arrangement For Transportation', 'We provide a door-to-door system where advance reservations are made to take an elderly individual from one place to another', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'arrangement-for-transportation-2', '', '', '2017-07-28 13:27:43', '2017-07-28 13:27:43', '', 0, 'http://goodsamalf.com/?post_type=goodsamservices&#038;p=240', 0, 'goodsamservices', '', 0),
(241, 1, '2017-06-29 04:15:09', '2017-06-29 04:15:09', '<a href="http://goodsamalf.com/goodsamservices/assistance-in-securing-healthcare-needs-2/"><u>Assistance for securing healthcare needs</u></a> are provided by our <a href="http://goodsamalf.com/goodsamservices/assistance-in-securing-healthcare-needs-2/"><u>licensed home care services agency</u></a>. These are located on our premises and operating under the direction of a registered nurse who works along with your physician in the development of your personal assisted living plan of care.', 'Assistance In Securing  Healthcare Needs', '<a href="http://goodsamalf.com/"><u>Assistance for securing healthcare</u></a> needs are provided by our licensed home care services agency located on our premises', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'assistance-in-securing-healthcare-needs-2', '', '', '2017-07-14 07:13:03', '2017-07-14 07:13:03', '', 0, 'http://goodsamalf.com/?post_type=goodsamservices&#038;p=241', 0, 'goodsamservices', '', 0),
