ny special functions or catering.</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1yf pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Oversee employees in the preparation of the next day''s menu and oversee the work as necessary.</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y10 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Maintain a clean and sanitary work area at all times. Clean and sanitize work station at the end of each shift.</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y11 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Keep reach-in refrigerators and freezer clean and organized with stored items dated and labeled per State of</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y12 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Florida Department of Health regulations</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y13 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Able to demonstrate ability to communicate effectively with residents, co-workers, Facility Manager and</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y14 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Administrator</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y15 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Communicates regularly with the Manager regarding problems with resident care, staffing problems and facility</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y16 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">environmental/maintenance concerns</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y17 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Demonstrates strong conflict resolution skills in a manner that is respectful and dignified.</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h7 pg-1y18 pg-1ff1 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">QUALIFICATIONS:</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y19 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Must have at least 2 years of cook experience..</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y1a pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Ability to read, speak and understand English.</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y1b pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Attention to detail, follow through and good interpersonal/problem solving ability</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y1c pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Formal cooking school training is a plus.</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y1d pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Must successfully pass a health screening including an approved tuberculosis test</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y1e pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Must successfully pass a Level 2 Background Screening</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y1f pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Good understanding of group home care</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y20 pg-1ff1 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">PHYSICAL/SENSORY REQUIREMENTS:<span class="pg-1ff2"> (with or without corrective devices)</span></div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y21 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Able to move continually throughout the facility during the work day</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y22 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Able to cope effectively with physical and mental performance elements</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y23 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Demonstrate emotional stability</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y24 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Able to lift, push, pull up to 50 pounds</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x4 pg-1h6 pg-1y25 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc1 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Hearing adequate to communicate with peers and residents</div>', 'Cook', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '466-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-07-10 23:40:56', '2017-07-10 23:40:56', '', 466, 'http://goodsamalf.com/466-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(468, 9, '2017-07-10 23:43:54', '2017-07-10 23:43:54', '<ul class="Reset">\r\n 	<li class="pageli">\r\n<div id="pf1" class="page-outer-wrapper">\r\n<div class="page-inner-wrapper">\r\n<div id="pg-1pf1" class="pf pg-1w0 pg-1h0">\r\n<div class="pc pg-1pc1 pg-1w0 pg-1h0">\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h4 pg-1y3 pg-1ff1 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">JOB DESCRIPTION</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h4 pg-1y4 pg-1ff1 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">JOB TITLE: Caregiver/MedTech</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h4 pg-1y5 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Department: Health Services</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h4 pg-1y6 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Supervised by: Administrator/Facility Manager</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h4 pg-1y7 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs2 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Supervises: None</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h2 pg-1y8 pg-1ff1 pg-1fs0 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Position Summary</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y9 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">This position provides assistance to residents with activities of daily living as well as medication management.</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1ya pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Emergency first aid may be required from time to time. Caregivers/Med Techs will be supervised by the Assisted Living</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1yb pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Facility Manager and the Assisted Living Facility Administrator.</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1yc pg-1ff1 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Essential Functions</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1yd pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Administer medications following established guidelines, policies and procedures, and state law</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1ye pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Assist residents with activities of daily living as specified in the residents service and care plan</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1yf pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Assist residents with bathing, dressing or undressing, grooming, transferring, toileting, and escort to and from</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y10 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">appointments and other destinations.</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y11 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Responsible for documenting in resident records any significant changes in residents condition and report such changes</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y12 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">to the Resident Services Director</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y13 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Take vital signs, including respirations, temperature, blood pressure and pulse and record information appropriately</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y14 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Responsible for participating in and supporting activity program</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y15 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Provide companionship to residents</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y16 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Monitor environment for safety or to maintain well-being of residents</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y17 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Report incidents to the Resident Services Director and/or Assisted Living Director using the appropriate forms</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y18 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Occasional light housekeeping, such as bed making and changing of linens</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y19 pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Participate in the development of the written service and care plan as requested by the resident</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y1a pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Ensure that the residents service and care plan is implemented</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y1b pg-1ff1 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">Organizational Functions</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y1c pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Ensure that medications are administered following physicians orders, established policy and procedure, and state law</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y1d pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Ensure that residents rights to fair and equitable treatment, self-determination, individuality, privacy, property, and civil</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y1e pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0">rights, including the right to file a complaint are upheld</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-1m0 pg-1x3 pg-1h5 pg-1y1f pg-1ff2 pg-1fs3 pg-1fc0 pg-1sc0 pg-1ls0 pg-1ws0"> Participates in and supports quality assurance/continuous quality improvement programs and processes</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></li>\r\n 	<li class="pageli">\r\n<div id="pf2" class="page-outer-wrapper">\r\n<div class="page-inner-wrapper">\r\n<div id="pg-2pf2" class="pf pg-2w0 pg-2h0">\r\n<div class="pc pg-2pc2 pg-2w0 pg-2h0">\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2y0 pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0"> Serves on standing and ad hoc work teams/committees as required</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x1 pg-2h1 pg-2y1 pg-2ff2 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0">Pg. 2 of 2</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2y2 pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0"> Attends all mandatory in-services as directed</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2y3 pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0"> Consistently maintains complete confidentiality of all medical, financial, employee, computer or other sensitive material</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2y4 pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0">which may jeopardize the privacy of others</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2y5 pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0"> Demonstrates orientation towards excellent customer service in all interactions by conducting oneself in a cooperative,</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2y6 pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0">courteous, positive, and professional manner</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2y7 pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0"> Displays sensitivity and awareness of others</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2y8 pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0"> Follows through with established expectations and keeps customers informed of progress</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2y9 pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0"> Supports, maintains, and promotes Beatitudes Mission Statement</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2ya pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0"> Performs other duties as requested or assigned</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2yb pg-2ff2 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0">Skills / Requirements</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2yc pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0"> Must be certified with current, valid CPR, 1st Aid &amp; Finger Print Clearance Card</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2yd pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0"> Prior medication experience a preferred</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2ye pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0"> Must be at least 18 years of age</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2yf pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0"> Strong desire to work with the elderly and care for their needs</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2y10 pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0"> Must be reliable and work extremely well independently, and as a team member</div>\r\n<div class="t pg-2m0 pg-2x0 pg-2h1 pg-2y11 pg-2ff1 pg-2fs0 pg-2fc0 pg-2sc0 pg-2ls0 pg-2ws0"> Ability to work with minimal supervision in a fast paced environment</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Med Tech', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'med-tech', '', '', '2017-07-10 23:46:17', '2017-07-10 23:46:17', '', 0, 'http://goodsamalf.com/?post_type=job&#038;p=468', 0, 'job', '', 0),
