(476, 9, '2017-07-10 23:51:21', '2017-07-10 23:51:21', '<strong>JOB DESCRIPTION</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>JOB TITLE: Maintenance</strong>\r\n\r\nDepartment: Environmental Services\r\n\r\nSupervised by: Facility Manager\r\n\r\nSupervises: None\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Description</strong>: Maintains all buildings and equipment throughout the facility and is required to perform the day-to-day functions of this position in accordance with current federal, state and local regulations as well as this facility''s established policies and procedures to assure that the facility is maintained in a safe, secure, and comfortable manner for our residents, staff and visitors.\r\n\r\nInterior/exterior building maintenance to include:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Painting, patching walls, replacing floor tiles</li>\r\n 	<li>Electrical repairs, bulb/ballast replacement</li>\r\n 	<li>Equipment repair and preventative maintenance, beds, wheelchairs, appliances, HVAC equipment</li>\r\n 	<li>Landscape care, mulch, lawn mowing, weeding, show shoveling, parking area and driveway sweeping</li>\r\n 	<li>Floor care to include carpet cleaning, floor stripping/finishing</li>\r\n 	<li>Handle Maintenance request for repairs and improvements</li>\r\n 	<li>Perform other duties/tasks as assigned</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>Education/Experience</strong>: High school diploma or GED required. At least one year training or equivalent experience in a maintenance/plant related position. Knowledge of basic plumbing, electrical and mechanical principals required\r\n\r\n<strong>Qualifications</strong>:\r\n\r\nMust have ability to follow written directions.\r\n\r\nDemonstrates good interpersonal and communication skills.\r\n\r\nMust be able to organize work activities with minimal supervision.\r\n\r\nMust be able to set priorities and plan workload independently.', 'Facility Maintenance', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'facility-maintenance', '', '', '2017-07-12 00:01:23', '2017-07-12 00:01:23', '', 0, 'http://goodsamalf.com/?post_type=job&#038;p=476', 0, 'job', '', 0),
